   '90d','strigoi-spin','2026-05-16 08:00:00+00','default'),
  ('a0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002','NVDA','NVIDIA Corp','PEAD',0.870,
   'Earnings beat by 14% YoY with raised guidance. Post-announcement drift in semiconductor sector with this magnitude historically correlates with 60-day continued upward drift in 7 of 10 comparable cases.',
   '["Q3 EPS +14% YoY, guidance raised for Q4","Unusual options activity: call volume 4× average in the 72 hours post-announcement","Options flow suggests institutional accumulation"]',
